item.title: CVE-2023-2288|2023-05-30T07:49:15.477Z -- unknown -- otter
item.description: The Otter WordPress plugin before 2.2.6 does not sanitize some user-controlled file paths before performing file operations on them. This leads to a PHAR deserialization vulnerability on PHP < 8.0 using the phar:// stream wrapper.
